"2010-07-20T20:55:02.187"	"5"	"92"	"The argument against this is that 0.99999999... is ""somewhat"" less than 1. How much exactly?\r\n\r\n          1 - 0.999999... = \u03b5\r\n\r\nIf the above is true, the following also must be true:\r\n\r\n    9 \xd7 (1 - 0.999999...) = \u03b5 \xd7 9\r\n\r\nLet's calculate:\r\n\r\n    0.999... \xd7\r\n    9        =\r\n    \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\r\n    8.1\r\n      81\r\n       81\r\n         .\r\n          .\r\n           .\r\n\r\n    \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\r\n    8.999...\r\n\r\nThus:\r\n\r\n         9 - 8.999999... = 9\u03b5              (1)\r\n\r\nBut:\r\n\r\n             8.999999... = 8 + 0.99999...  (2)\r\n\r\nIndeed:\r\n\r\n    8.00000000... +\r\n    0.99999999... =\r\n    \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\r\n    8.99999999...\r\n\r\nNow let's see what we can deduce from `(1)` and `(2)`.\r\n\r\n    9 - 8.999999... = 9\u03b5\r\n    9 - 8.999999... = 9 - (8 + 0.99999...) =\r\n                    = 9 -  8 - (1 - \u03b5)\r\n                    =   1    -  1 + \u03b5\r\n                    =               \u03b5.\r\n\r\nThus:\r\n\r\n    9\u03b5 = \u03b5\r\n\r\n    10\u03b5 = 0\r\n\r\n    \u03b5 = 0\r\n\r\n    1 - 0.999999... = \u03b5 = 0\r\n\r\nQuod erat dimostrandum. Pardon my unicode."	"32472923-4984-4e04-9af4-5a9d20427e7d"	"110"	"216"	"added 1 characters in body"	""	""
